OL,6,FA husband and wife who died in a crash
OL,7,Fin the Scottish Borders have been
OL,8,Fnamed.
OL,10,FThe incident happened on the A703 just
OL,11,Fbefore the junction for Waterheads
OL,12,Faround nd involved a grey Nissan Note
OL,13,Fand a white Ford Kuga.
OL,15,FEmergency services attended and the
OL,16,Fpassenger of the Nissan, an 86-year-
OL,17,Fold man, later named David Fletcher
OL,18,Ffrom the Penicuik area, was pronounced
OL,19,Fdead at the scene.
