OL,6,FHis wife, Margaret Fletcher, 82, was
OL,7,Fdriving the Nissan and was taken to
OL,8,Fthe Royal Infirmary of Edinburgh where
OL,9,Fshe died on Tuesday 27 February.
OL,11,FThe driver of the Ford, a 40-year-old
OL,12,Fman, was also taken to the Royal
OL,13,FInfirmary of Edinburgh for treatment
OL,14,Fand later released.
OL,16,FThe road was closed while
OL,17,Finvestigations were carried out and
OL,18,Freopened around 9pm.
