OL,6,FSergeant Barry Sommerville of Lothians
OL,7,Fand Borders Road Policing said: "Our
OL,8,Fthoughts continue to be with the
OL,9,Ffamily and friends of the couple who
OL,10,Fdied and they have asked for privacy
OL,11,Fat what is a very difficult time for
OL,12,Fall.
OL,14,F"Our enquiries are ongoing to
OL,15,Festablish the full circumstances and
OL,16,Fwe are appealing for anyone who has
OL,17,Fnot already spoken to officers to get
OL,18,Fin touch, particularly if you have
OL,19,Fdash-cam that could assist."
